name: LehinaModel - v1.1
description:
Please put an objective assessment of my work ⭑, it will motivate me to make new models.

Check the version description below (bottom right) for more info and add a ❤️ to receive future updates.

ENG:

Negative key (recommend):
comedone, skin cancer, psoriasis, eczema, herpes

Full Negative prompt (recommend):
layman work, worst quality, ugly, (deformed|distorted|disfigured:1.21), poorly drawn, bad anatomy, wrong anatomy, mutation, mutated, (mutated hands AND fingers:1.21), bad hands, bad fingers,loss of a limb, extra limb, missing limb, floating limbs, amputation, Yaeba, hat, cap, foam, comedone, skin cancer, psoriasis, eczema, herpes

LehinaModel:

Universal Stable Diffusion model with predisposition towards photorealism.

  1. Another step towards photorealism.

  2. Wide range of skin tones.

  3. Recognises dozens of ethnicities.

  4. Different graduation of skin tones for Asian, African, and European features.

  5. Even better perception of light and shadow.

  6. The function "Restore faces" isn't needed in 98% of generated outcomes.

For comparisons with other top models see: ⤸

(all prompts are taken from civitai, without the use of LoRA)

Enjoy creating art for yourself and your loved ones.

RUS:

LehinaModel:

Универсальная модель для Stable Diffusion с уклоном на фотореализм.

  1. Ещё один шаг к фотореализму.

  2. Широкий диапазон тонов кожи.

  3. Понимает десятки этносов.

  4. Разная градация тонов кожи для азиаткой, африканской, европейской внешности.

  5. Ещё лучше воспринимает свето-тени.

  6. В 98% генераций функция "Restore faces" не требуется.

Сравнение с другими топовыми моделями можно посмотреть тут: ⤸

(все подсказки взяты с civitai, без применения LoRA)
